Final Project: Content Creators and Streaming Services

How do traditional entertainment parent-company powerhouses (Disney, ATT, Comcast) stack up against today’s entertainment streaming services? (Netflix, Amazon)

Business Questions:

  1. How has the entertainment industry changed with the addition of streaming media services?
  2. Has the “content production and distribution” side of the industry changed with competition from Netflix and Amazon?
  3. Is there a future for non-streaming media companies?
